                    </thead>
                    <tbody valign="top">
                        <row>
                            <entry>
                                <para>
                                    <emph type="bold">THREAD LOCKING -</emph>Locks/Seals differential and transmission
                                    drain, fill and temperature sending plugs, lock nuts, bolts, screws and other
                                    fasteners. Seals to form a leakproof assembly against air, fuel and hydraulic leaks.
                                    Cures rapidly and easily disassembled with hand tools.
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>General Purpose Lock N' Seal&#174; #242</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Blue</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>6 ml</para>
                                <para>18 ml</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>577588-C1*</para>
                                <para>577589-C1*</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Extra strength adhesive for large fasteners and heavy duty parts. Seals against
                                    air, oil, air conditioning and hydraulic leaks. Locks/Seals differential capscrews,
                                    case bolts and studs, power divider mounting bolts. Locks Rockwell differential
                                    carrier bearing cap bolts. May require extra effort for disassembly.
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Heavy Duty Lock N' Seal&#174; #277</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Red</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>6 ml</para>
                                <para>18 ml</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>576016C1*</para>
                                <para>576017C1*</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>
                                <para>
                                    <emph type="bold">SEALING -</emph>Seals fuel, water, gas and hydraulic fittings,
                                    threaded vacuum line connectors and air brake line connections instantly. Easily
                                    removable with hand tools.
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Pipe Sealant w/Teflon&#174;</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>White</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>6 mi</para>
                                <para>36 ml</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>554209C1*</para>
                                <para>554211C1*</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Seals, protects electrical connections and wiring from salt, dirt and corrosion.
                                    Prevents voltage leakage at connections and excellent for the sealing of air cleaner
                                    elements.
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Dielectric Tune-Up Grease</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Clear</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>3 oz</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>2501657C1</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Seals oil pan, transmission and timing cover gaskets. Seals hose connections and
                                    threaded assemblies. Non-hardening.
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Make-A- Gasket&#174; #2</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Grayish</para>
                                <para>Brown</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>3 oz.</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>554206C1</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>
                                <para>
                                    <emph type="bold">RETAINING OR MOUNTING PARTS</emph>
                                    - Seals and mounts cup plugs, gears, bushings and oil seals. Restores press fits and
                                    prevents leakage.
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Sleeve and Bearing Mount #609</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Green</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>18 ml</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>554210C1*</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>
                                <para>
                                    <emph type="bold">GASKETING</emph>
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Superflex&#8482; RTV #595 Silicone</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Clear</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>3 oz.</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>554204C1</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Seals and repairs weather stripping, insulates and oil seals engine oil pan and
                                    valve cover gaskets. Special applications are rear axle cover, output shaft
                                    retainer, axle shaft ranges, differential carrier to axle housing and power divider
                                    intermediate case to main carrier housing mounting surface. Stays flexible. NOTE:
                                    Once RTV silicone sealant has been installed, parts must be assembled before sealant
                                    starts to set-up.
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>RTV Silicone by Dow Corning &#38; General Electric</para>
                                <para>Form-A-Gasket #593</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Black</para>
                                <para>Black</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>4.7 oz</para>
                                <para>7 oz.</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>446839C1</para>
                                <para>991443C1</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Self-seating gasket. Low volatility. Non-corrosive to electrical contact
                                    components such as speed shift motor cover. Will not harm aluminum, iron, plastic or
                                    steel.
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Ultra Blue&#8482; No Leak Silicone&#8482; Gasket #587</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Blue</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>3 oz.</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>1653885C1*</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Use where Gasket Eliminator&#174; #515 is specified.</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Gasket Eliminator&#174; #515</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Purple</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>50 ml</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>474517C2*</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Seals differential assemblies to rear axle housing, rear axle shaft range shifter,
                                    transmission cover and power dividers. Replaces cut gaskets; easily removed. To be
                                    used on Spicer heavy axles.
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Gasket Eliminator&#174; #518</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Red</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>6 ml</para>
                                <para>50 ml</para>
                                <para>250 ml</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>1693855C1</para>
                                <para>1693856C1</para>
                                <para>1693857C1</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>
                                <para>All-purpose adhesive which sets fast to hold gaskets in place, yet permits moving
                                    for alignment. Holds and seats felt, cork, metal, paper, rubber gaskets. Resists
                                    gasoline, oil, kerosene, propane and butane.
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>High Tack Adhesive Sealant #98D</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Red</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>16 oz. Brush Can</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>991445C1</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>
                                <para>
                                    <emph type="bold">BONDING</emph>
                                    - Bonds loose vinyl trim, weather stripping, appointments, name plates and body side
                                    molding.
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Gelmatic&#174; Instant Adhesive #21937</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Clear</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>5 ml</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>2501622C1</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Bonds rearview mirror to windshield and window toggles to glass.</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Rearview Mirror Adhesive #312</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Amber</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>.5 ml (one repair)</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>554212C1</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>
                                <para>A professional quality, black super weatherstrip adhesive. Fast drying and blends
                                    with black automotive weatherstrip for less clean-up. High strength.
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Super Weatherstrip Adhesive #82</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Black</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>5 oz.</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>991444C1</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Strips form-in-place gaskets, baked gaskets, dried oil, grease and paint. Removes
                                    carbon deposits from valves, heads and pistons.
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Gasket Remover #4MA</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para></para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>10.75 oz.</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>554259C1</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>
                                <para>
                                    <emph type="bold">LUBRICANTS</emph>
                                    - Anti-seize lubricant which prevents seizing, galling, pitting and corrosion of
                                    metal parts exposed to extreme temperatures or corrosive atmospheres. For use on
                                    wheel bolts and nuts, cables, chains, exhausts manifold bolts, spark plugs and
                                    hinges.
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Anti-Seize Lubricant</para>
                                <para>#767</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Gray</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>16 oz. Brush Top</para>
                                <para>16 oz. Aerosol</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>991441C1</para>
                                <para>991442C1</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry colspan="5" spanname="1to5">
                                <para>*It is suggested that Clean N' Cure Primer be used. Refer to CLEANERS, in this
                                    table.
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                    </tbody>
                </tgroup>
            </table>
            <specpara>
                <important>
                    <para>For sealants to bond properly, it is essential that surfaces are clean, free of oil residue
                        and all instructions are followed closely.
                    </para>
                </important>
            </specpara>
            <para></para>
            <para></para>
            <para></para>
